{"tid":1549743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母講幾多次先明呀 冇屍體就係失蹤 有屍就係死人","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:32:45.000Z","uid":53361,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d788f1c611b96e432d96d8686f35d3d58d6a91","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"失蹤就係失蹤<br />\n死人就係死人<br />\n<br />\n失蹤其實仲嚴重過死人<br />\n因為係存心隱瞞事實<br />\n正常人睇都會知咩事啦<br />\n總之黑警一日唔俾證據出嚟就係失蹤<br />\n唔洗再拗<br />\n推行動做文宣啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有聽日出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8175e28f4e206e8129eb6dc307f5dbe49bebe33","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:20:42.000Z","msg":"失蹤呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55891248fea9afef019939192bf2a42fff7f09ae","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"揾唔到個女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8953536f54eafba42c3b045affd185a65c276de","tid":1549743,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca311b8ea42e4bdbbcb88c8afb825d385387f07a","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"個仔唔見左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170e2fa75e855707184ff2238ac962e24f2cfa8a","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"冇死人 不過揾唔返仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe6e9f2d2e0f5ad243592125542b53e84734921","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"佢幾日冇返過屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61a5d73239af03e7a8c97d7315cff3f95daf4b0","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"打電話都揾佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6430edd73680290191a3cc0b219bc953a7bebe","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"朋友都話冇見過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29267c1c5ebbb02207836995c5655d11eb056940","tid":1549743,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38a953314d641ecd1491f6ec8f43e81531260b65","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"唔敢向警察報案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da98d6744e1447ee2bc4267b74fce04eadb51686","tid":1549743,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"6fc117352818b2e6ffa2160ca575066276925114","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"交CCTV 還我仔女清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da51561988b2e68e981903ea0f77e1b4cf0928eb","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"3人仍然失蹤<br />\n3 are still missing<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd0426487ddc3108c6233a49aa81eab6e4a6538","tid":1549743,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"3 are still missing<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}